<subSubSection pageId="136" pageNumber="533" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="136.[116,1323,1714,2377]" pageId="136" pageNumber="533">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[119,472,2226,2259]" pageId="136" pageNumber="533">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Virtually nothing is known of the Heather White-toothed Shrew. It is probably threatened by habitat loss and fragmentation from agricultural expansion.
</paragraph>
